---
<section id="education" class="max-w-[1100px] mx-auto px-10 pb-24">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-12">
    <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.1em]">
      <span data-lang="en">Education</span>
      <span data-lang="de">Studium</span>
    </span>
    <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-border"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-col">

    <!-- M.Sc. -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[80px_1fr] gap-6 py-7 border-t border-border">
      <div class="font-mono text-xs text-muted pt-1">
        <span data-lang="en">2019 — 2022</span>
        <span data-lang="de">2019 — 2022</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="font-mono text-[10px] text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.1em] mb-1.5">
          <span data-lang="en">M.Sc. Computer Science</span>
          <span data-lang="de">M.Sc. Informatik</span>
        </div>
        <div class="font-serif text-lg font-normal tracking-[-0.01em] leading-snug mb-2">
          <a
            href="https://www.haw-hamburg.de/en/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="hover:text-accent transition-colors"
            aria-label="Hamburg University of Applied Sciences (opens in new tab)"
          >
            <span data-lang="en">Hamburg University of Applied Sciences (HAW Hamburg)</span>
            <span data-lang="de">Hochschule für Angewandte Wissenschaften Hamburg (HAW Hamburg)</span>
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mb-1">
          <span data-lang="en">Focus: Multilingual NLP · Recommender Systems · Transformer Models</span>
          <span data-lang="de">Schwerpunkte: Multilinguale Sprachverarbeitung · Empfehlungssysteme · Transformer-Modelle</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
          <span data-lang="en">
            Thesis: Language-agnostic sequence-based news recommender trained on 313M+ pageviews;
            evaluated via A/B test with CTR as primary KPI.
          </span>
          <span data-lang="de">
            Masterarbeit: Sprachagnostischer, sequenzbasierter Nachrichtenempfehlungsalgorithmus;
            Training auf 313 Mio.+ Seitenaufrufen, Evaluierung per A/B-Test mit CTR als primärer Kennzahl.
          </span>
          {' '}
          <a
            href="https://reposit.haw-hamburg.de/handle/20.500.12738/16167"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-accent hover:underline font-mono text-[11px]"
            aria-label="Master thesis publication (opens in new tab)"
          >
            Publication ↗
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- B.Sc. -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[80px_1fr] gap-6 py-7 border-t border-border border-b">
      <div class="font-mono text-xs text-muted pt-1">
        <span data-lang="en">2014 — 2019</span>
        <span data-lang="de">2014 — 2019</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="font-mono text-[10px] text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.1em] mb-1.5">
          <span data-lang="en">B.Sc. Computer Science</span>
          <span data-lang="de">B.Sc. Informatik</span>
        </div>
        <div class="font-serif text-lg font-normal tracking-[-0.01em] leading-snug mb-2">
          <a
            href="https://www.haw-hamburg.de/en/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="hover:text-accent transition-colors"
            aria-label="Hamburg University of Applied Sciences (opens in new tab)"
          >
            <span data-lang="en">Hamburg University of Applied Sciences (HAW Hamburg)</span>
            <span data-lang="de">Hochschule für Angewandte Wissenschaften Hamburg (HAW Hamburg)</span>
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
          <span data-lang="en">
            Thesis: Text Classification via BERT-based Text Splitting Controlled by a Search Algorithm.
          </span>
          <span data-lang="de">
            Bachelorarbeit: Textsegmentierung per BFS-Algorithmus über BERT's Next-Sentence-Prediction zur verbesserten Klassifikation kolloquialer Texte.
          </span>
          {' '}
          <a
            href="https://reposit.haw-hamburg.de/handle/20.500.12738/14496"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-accent hover:underline font-mono text-[11px]"
            aria-label="Bachelor thesis publication (opens in new tab)"
          >
            Publication ↗
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
